dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.genericstructure.varianthandling

Interface IPostBuildVariantCriterionValue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IPostBuildVariantCriterionValue
extends IEntity
    IPostBuildVariantCriterionValue: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This class specifies the value which shall be assigned to a particular variant criterion in order to bind the variation point. If multiple criterion/value pairs are specified, they all shall match to bind the variation point.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
